text: Your dream home just hit the market! Welcome to 21359 Egret Place in the gorgeous Cedar Ridge Estate Community. Here you will find main floor living with large basement (MIL potential!), two living spaces with a wood burning & gas fireplaces, a lovely formal dining room, an oversized office with French doors, Brazilian cherry hardwood floors, 4 bedrooms/3.5 bathrooms, a gorgeous 1.33 acre lot and more! An entertainers paradise, fall in love with the beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & walk-in pantry. The kitchen flows to your bright living area and outdoor deck. Stay cozy during the winters with radiant floor heating & cool during the summer with AC. A 3 minute walk to neighborhood private lake access!

44' moorage slip located in Skyline Marina, just minutes from downtown Anacortes. Skyline Marina is the gateway to San Juan Islands, with the shortest run into the islands of any marina. Skyline is a full service marina with fuel, chandlery, repair, dry storage, and hoist/launch facilities, yacht club. You will find: restrooms, showers, laundry facilities, groceries and ice, garbage receptacles, ample parking. Sold as-is. Slip is 44' in length and 16.3' wide.

Nestled in the picturesque Shelter Bay community, take the opportunity to fully embrace the tranquil & distinctive lifestyle it offers. Make this charming 2 lot, home your retreat, enjoying its peaceful & secluded setting with plenty of parking space. The home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 1.75 baths & a single-car garage with compact workshop space. Delight in the expansive windows throughout while staying comfortably cool with the modern mini-split ductless heat pump, ensuring ideal climate control. Indulge in the array of community amenities, including access to 2 private beaches, a clubhouse for gatherings, a marina complete with a boat ramp, a swimming pool, a tennis court for recreation, & a BBQ area perfect for outdoor entertaining.

Wake to a Skagit Valley sunrise. Enjoy mornings overlooking tulip and daffodil fields in the Spring, with Mount Baker and the Cascades in the background. This custom-designed home was built by current owners in 2016. It sits on a 3.6 acre property on the highly desired Pleasant Ridge overlooking Skagit Valley. The home is designed for main level living and comfort. Featuring two primary bedroom suites, vaulted ceilings, beautiful wood trim, heated polished concrete floors throughout - even a steam shower! Plus, a loft office or art studio space with deck. All rooms focus your attention on the commanding view over the Valley. Over 1.5 acres of fenced pasture, gated pens and shelters, all provide a perfect environment for your farm animals!

This charming single-story home is the perfect starter home for those seeking comfort, convenience and modern amenities. Natural light streams in through the living area. Adjacent to the living room is the modern kitchen w/eating area. The primary bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom while the home features two additional cozy bedrooms plus a second full bathroom with a tub/shower combo. Central air conditioning ensures year-round comfort, allowing you to escape the summer heat and stay cozy in the winter months. An attached 2 car garage provides convenient parking and additional storage space for bikes, tools, and outdoor gear. Just minutes away from all that Mount Vernon has to offer & makes commuting to nearby cities a breeze. Turn key!

Experience the breathtaking beauty of Anacortes Forestlands from the comfort of a custom-built home perched atop the Rock Ridge neighborhood. This PNW modern home is a celebration of style and functionality. With step-less main level living, a generously sized kitchen featuring high-end appliances, an island, and stunning neutral finishes, this home offers an unparalleled living experience. The primary bedroom and en-suite on the main floor come complete with a walk-in shower, free-standing tub, and double sinks, allowing you to unwind in luxurious comfort. Main level private office. Downstairs, three bedrooms, a rec room, and a third bathroom make this home spacious and inviting. Moreover, a large unfinished bonus room with outdoor access.

Nestled in a serene and secluded setting, this renovated chalet-style home radiates sophistication. Featuring vaulted ceilings, it offers two generously-sized master suites and two baths. The residence features new vinyl plank flooring throughout and a new kitchen with tile backsplash.Freshly painted inside and out, the residence comes complete with a new deck, providing a perfect retreat to enjoy the surrounding nature. Additionally, a detached one-car garage, RV parking, and outbuildings offer abundant storage. This property seamlessly combines contemporary elegance with natural charm creating an idyllic retreat for refined living.

Dont miss this beautiful home! This meticulously maintained property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, including 2 primary suites, both with walk in showers and one with a large walk-in closet. The living room features a cozy gas fireplace, and bay windows for lots of natural light. The updated kitchen with modern appliances and ample counter space is sure to impress. Step outside to discover a fully fenced yard with a covered patio, ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying your morning coffee in peace. The low maintenance yard with AstroTurf allows you to relax and unwind without the hassle of constant upkeep. Plus, two car attached garage and RV parking . Don't miss out on this opportunity to call this place home!

Beautiful, flat one acre lot, Space for RV / Boat Parking or add a shop. 3 Car Tandem garage. Neighborhood is gated for added security and privacy and is adjacent to Rasar State Park with great access to the Skagit River and extensive walking trails. The home is completed with maple cabinets, LVP floors, slab granite counters, full height backsplash, white painted millwork, wood wrapped windows, double panel white painted doors and stainless steel appliances. High ceilings in the huge family room, formal dining room, downstairs office and a huge master bedroom make this home extremely functional. Hybrid heat pump water heater, High Efficiency ductless mini splits provide both heating and air conditioning to the entire living area.

Welcome to your dream home! This charming single-level residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.75 bathrooms, and a well-maintained interior. Enjoy the convenience of a 924-square-foot unfinished basement, perfect for storage or future expansion, with both interior and exterior access. The sunny and flat .4-acre lot offers ample space for outdoor activities, complemented by a wood shed and storage shed. With a nice double-car garage, ample parking, and a drive-through driveway, this home offers both convenience and comfort. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own your slice of paradise!

Excellent investment opportunity! This duplex features two units that each have 2 bedrooms & 1 bathroom as well as laundry in each. This two unit home sits on a large open lot with lots of parking and beautiful views of the valley, mountains, and sunsets. They are extremely well maintained. Don't miss out on this great opportunity to begin or expand your real estate investments.

Welcome to this charming home in the desirable Hillcrest neighborhood! This cozy 1, 144 SF rambler offers comfort and convenience and is only a block away from Hillcrest Park. Boasting 2 BD, 1 BA, and a bonus room w/ back porch entrance, this home provides ample space for relaxation and entertaining. Enjoy the benefits of vinyl windows, ceiling fans throughout, and a gas furnace with forced air heating for year-round comfort. The cute dining area off the kitchen adds a touch of charm to mealtimes. Outside, a shed with electricity and heat provides the perfect space for hobbies or yard tools. Fully fenced backyard. Great location close to schools, medical, downtown, park, & I-5 for easy commuting.

This Sedro-Woolley acreage is just what you've been waiting for! 5.22 Acres with mix of pasture and trees on quiet road just outside of town. Owner has done most of the preliminary work for you with pasture fencing, gates, driveway install and new drilled well by Dahlman well drilling. PSE power vault on property. Neighboring septic systems are gravity systems. Bring your building plans and septic design or place a manufactured home and live the rural life you've been dreaming of!

Amazing fresh and bright rambler in highly desirable established neighborhood on quiet dead-end street. Close to college, school, parks & services, this location complete with mountain views, & 2-car garage. Home features: Vaulted ceilings, light filled living areas, and gas stove. Massive back deck area is perfect for entertaining. Huge park like backyard with plenty of room for gardening, pets, and parking. Quality upgrades include newer AC, gas furnace, & gas water heater. Primary bedroom has attached bathroom. Oversize RV & Boat parking. Shed for extra storage.

Beautiful light and bright 1901 home with modern updates and hints of historic charm. Updates include new solar panels, water heater, podcasting/gaming room with sound proofing, full kitchen remodel including cabinets, quartz countertops, stove and refrigerator. Main level has a wood insert fireplace, living & family rooms, dedicated home office, full bath, and Primary Bdrm. Upstairs are 2 bdrms and a bonus room. Lower level is fully finished with 4th bdrm, hobby/shop room, cellar, tons of storage, new carpeting, 1/2 bath, laundry, and large rec area. Backyard is a gardener's dream with irrigated raised beds, fruit trees, greenhouse, chicken coop and utility shed. Minutes to Downtown, Hospital, schools, groceries, restaurants, and parks.

Nestled within the coveted Windward Village, this Northwest contemporary home epitomizes refined living in the center of Anacortes. With its open concept design and high end finishes on the main level, it features a gourmet kitchen with a double oven, cooktop, and granite counters for a true dining experience, complemented by vaulted ceilings and a private courtyard for entertainment. A primary bedroom suite offers a full bath retreat. Downstairs, two bedrooms and family room provide ample space for living and enjoyment. The mature landscaping, complete with a custom-designed rock pathway leading to the fish pond and steps through the front yard, beckons with gardening opportunities. Experience serenity and luxury in this exceptional home.

Introducing a new construction single-level home by Landed Gentry. Our Warner plan is just beautiful! It has 1, 368 sf, but feels much larger. Featuring 2 bedrooms PLUS a study/3rd bedroom and 1.75 bath. The central living area includes vaulted ceiling and expansive luxury vinyl plank throughout the entry/living/kitchen/dining areas/laundry. Finishes include white cabinetry, granite counters, tile accents and ss appliances. Home is fully landscaped with fenced rear yard and its on a quiet, dead-end street. The home is just a 2 minute drive to local restaurants & grocery stores and an 8 minute drive to Riverfront Park. Move in ready! Come see.

Breathtaking water view rambler! Enjoy views of Burrows Bay from most windows. Step out onto the new Trex deck and engulf yourself in the stunning water views. With a newly remodeled exterior including new siding and paint. This home offers vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan for spacious living. Enjoy gardening in your very own garden. With Tugboat Beach is only steps away and Skyline Marina within a mile of your home, this is true beach living. Skyline amenities including pickleball courts, tennis courts, beach cabana, Skyline clubhouse and more. Home is sold as-is.

Check out this beautifully upgraded Mt Baker view condo! The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances and elegant granite counters. Gas fireplace offers a unique and inviting ambiance that combines warmth, convenience and visual appeal. This condo is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, elegance and scenic beauty. Schedule a showing today and discover the potential for your new chapter in this charming residence.

Undisputed best opportunity in Mount Vernon. Freshly remodeled rambler brings all the convenience of modern living while maintaining its classic charm. Detached garage. Conveniently located close to downtown Mount Vernon with all the restaurants and entertainment. Easy access to I-5. Don't miss your shot at this amazing home!

A truly move-in ready rambler in Sedro-Woolley is calling you! Step onto the covered front porch and through the tiled entry, onto gleaming Brazilian Cherry hardwood floors. Check out the vaulted ceilings and lovely tiled gas fireplace in the great room off the kitchen, which features granite countertops and clean white cabinetry. Custom built-ins and woodwork flank the fireplace, and French doors lead out to a freshly-painted back deck. The updates continue with a brand-new water heater, brand new carpets in all three bedrooms, and newly-refreshed bathrooms. Easy access to both Highway 20 and Highway 9 make for a great commute. Don't miss this one!

Nestled down a private lane in Sedro Woolley, this charming PRE-INSPECTED historic home offers a spacious backyard with fruit trees, berry bushes, and garden space. On over half an acre, this property is a unique opportunity for equity and growth. The garage and workshop offer space for projects and ample storage. Updates throughout the home preserve its essential character. A new tankless water heater provides endless hot water, while a new high efficiency wood stove insert makes this home cozy. Comes with a 1-year seller-paid home warranty and NO HOA.

Light and bright, well-maintained move in ready open concept with a 30 x 40 shop. Tons of natural light throughout the house including a 4 seasons sunroom where you can enjoy coffee and watch the deer and also an extra bonus room. The back yard is your own private sanctuary and partially fenced. Stainless steel appliances stay. The shop is fully enclosed with parking for 2 cars plus extra space for all your projects or toys. Very close to schools, fire department and services
